168b90fe649dea2276a0fef79c0d76734","tid":2421732,"uid":261914,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T21:42:32.000Z","msg":"真，不過其實都係自己覺得<br />\n<br />\n但最慘既係現實比人講，<br />\n&ldquo;呀，你都係影相好睇d&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80a5f461dab3a7eb356183b1edb73ce601c4fee1","tid":2421732,"uid":384113,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"8152158b48525dbbf8eef2bdb9a223fb0fcfbe68","tid":2421732,"uid":26106,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"6cfc37884ed331d12c0fa394523974a644bf47e1","tid":2421732,"uid":384113,"like":11,"dislike":53,"score":-42,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T16:55:15.000Z","msg":"其實你影相個樣等於人地望你個樣"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T21:10:43.000Z","msg":"緊係唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n淨係人眼像素同感光 同相機已經差好遠啦<br />\n已經未計角度 立體感"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T21:50:59.000Z","msg":"人望自己 通常都會跟住好睇既方向去望 加上上望得多習慣咗 所以自然覺得鏡入邊嘅自己好睇過影相"},{"pid":"a20a3d14345fca94b15c177c101bc3735f2a8d97","tid":2421732,"uid":175870,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T23:34:55.000Z","msg":"但我都有見過真人靚過相既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要係靚好多<br />\n佢本身顴骨偏大/高 影出黎一般<br />\n真人睇顴骨又冇咁突出 又有氣質"},{"pid":"f4c53eb0d1e252ef1ed0ef90e508d460937f0d6c","tid":2421732,"uid":51033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f40ff261c455c9ae5142e9f18cfd73ab1efc1dbb","tid":2421732,"uid":51594,"like":90,"dislike":0,"score":90,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T17:01:02.000Z","msg":"同照鏡個樣差太遠 次次都比相入面嘅自己嚇親<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n慢慢就怕左影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T23:37:02.000Z","msg":"所以從來都唔俾人影我<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b9a243298e10d93fedff0ffc558e742e092a44a","tid":2421732,"uid":60031,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T23:52:29.000Z","msg":"影相同照鏡左右調轉，所以會睇唔慣。<br />\n<br />\n樣衰左有解釋。<br />\n<br />\n人睇野用2隻眼，左右眼用2個唔同角度望，2個影像再由大腦合成，係3D有深度。<br />\n<br />\n但影相得1個鏡頭，1個角度，再由3D變2D，姐係塊面既深度弧角會比部相拉到變平面，令到塊面睇落扁啲、闊啲，好似肥左10磅咁，識影相既人會就番角度彌補2D既問題，另外再化重妝打影先做到廣告相咁靚。<br />\n<br />\n另外，人平時有表情會郁，定鏡係會怪左，你試下睇戲突然定格，啲明星都會變怪樣。有好多人影相緊張唔識表情管理，就會整左個弱智樣出黎。"},{"pid":"2a0263fa7121af3641321a63867d19d3edd36138","tid":2421732,"uid":361753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6cfc37884ed331d12c0fa394523974a644bf47e1","tid":2421732,"uid":384113,"like":11,"dislike":53,"score":-42,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T16:55:15.000Z","msg":"其實你影相個樣等於人地望你個樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T23:58:22.000Z","msg":"P牌 鳩up <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac15dff7947253c51fc0ba85116ccdc93945e7f6","tid":2421732,"uid":197762,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T00:03:34.000Z","msg":"你係樣衰點影都係樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a08fb1fbe4f42ccede29d04ae3d09d58ee1b981","tid":2421732,"uid":50513,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a20a3d14345fca94b15c177c101bc3735f2a8d97","tid":2421732,"uid":175870,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T23:34:55.000Z","msg":"但我都有見過真人靚過相既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要係靚好多<br />\n佢本身顴骨偏大/高 影出黎一般<br />\n真人睇顴骨又冇咁突出 又有氣質"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T00:07:40.000Z","msg":"我都識人係咁 真人勁靚女但一影相就變到好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34970a72a476081b7506a2846d46b6196dd96173","tid":2421732,"uid":83335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cfc37884ed331d12c0fa394523974a644bf47e1","tid":2421732,"uid":384113,"like":11,"dislike":53,"score":-42,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"202